    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride? I'm parting with my car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs beautifully, and has been well-maintained over the years. It's perfect for your daily commute or those fun weekend road trips. You're going to love how it handles! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great new home!",
