    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable and well-presented car. The exterior is finished in a timeless coat that still holds a high gloss, showing only the expected minor stone chips on the front fascia from highway driving. Moving inside, the interior has been kept in excellent shape; the upholstery is free of tears or stains, and the dashboard remains crack-free. Every power option, including the sunroof, heated seats, and premium audio system, is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs quietly, benefited by a documented history of synthetic oil changes and recent fluid flushes. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the suspension provides a smooth, rattle-free ride. It is a dependable, turn-key vehicle that has been treated with care and is ready for many more miles of service.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been curated for the driver who demands both reliability and presence. It exhibits a commendable level of care, featuring a robust powertrain and an interior that remains remarkably well-appointed. This offering provides an optimal balance of value and prestige, ensuring a confident acquisition for its next proprietor.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
